bidden+Love+%28novel%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Forbidden_Love_(novel)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Related articles:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.publishersweekly.com/article/CA440780.html?pubdate=8%2F2%2F2004&amp;display=archive\"><i>Publishers Weekly</i></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.city-journal.org/html/eon_2_14_03kh.html\"><i>City Journal</i></a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2170\nCached time: 20180915070939\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.080 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.112 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 185/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 4714/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 3/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 3879/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.038/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1.91 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   84.987      1 -total\n 54.10%   45.979      3 Template:Cite_news\n 25.03%   21.270      1 Template:Italic_title\n 12.45%   10.584      1 Template:Main\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:1041136-0!canonical and timestamp 20180915070938 and revision id 839761195\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"Forbidden Love (Novel)","*":"2003_novels"},{"sortkey":"Forbidden Love (Novel)","*":"Literary_forgeries"},{"